      • directDependencies

        @Nonnull
public Stream<AtomicDecomposition.Atom> directDependencies()
        Returns the AtomicDecomposition.Atoms this AtomicDecomposition.Atom DIRECTLY depends on, excluding this atom. In the literature, all atoms (A) with (this) &gt; (A), such there is no other atom (B) with (this) &gt; (B) &gt; (A). This method is equal to calling thisAtom.dependencies(thisAtom::directlyDependsOn) and on each call is in O(this.getAxiomCount()^2) .
        Returns:
        The AtomicDecomposition.Atoms this AtomicDecomposition.Atom DIRECTLY depends on, excluding this atom
